InviteHelp:
1. If you recommend users to add a fund pool, you can get extra reward weight;
2. Direct recommendation, get 50% of the weight of the fund pool added by the directly recommended user;
3. Indirect recommendation, get 25% of the weight of the fund pool added by indirect recommended users.
